description:
The GNOME Project released today GNOME 46.3 as the third maintenance update to the latest GNOME 46 “Kathmandu” desktop environment series, bringing more bug fixes and small improvements.

The post GNOME 46.3 Desktop Environment Released With Various Improvements appeared first on Linux Today.
title: GNOME 46.3 Desktop Environment Released With Various Improvements
